  "3029180": {
    "name": "Kingdomino",
    "steam_appid": 3029180,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一名前来寻找新土地、为自己的王国开疆拓土的领主。你必须领略麦田、湖泊、山地等各种地形，找出最具价值的土地；同时你将与其他领主展开争夺，看谁能抢先将其收入囊中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏为实体桌游《多米诺王国》的官方改编游戏，该原作曾荣获 2017 年德国年度游戏奖（Spiel des Jahres）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029180/extras/10aee57cc2b3512fa8aa9aec073b0a98.avif?t=1768833137\" width=614 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029180/extras/af15dcca63e01ed6e41324a92500c08c.poster.avif?t=1768833137\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029180/extras/af15dcca63e01ed6e41324a92500c08c.webm?t=1768833137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029180/extras/af15dcca63e01ed6e41324a92500c08c.mp4?t=1768833137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以与机智的 AI 对手一较高下，又或加入多人对局比拼智慧，也可以跟你的好友组队游玩；可以挑战专为硬核策略爱好者准备的 7x7 巅峰对决模式，亦或完成 15+ 个独特的任务挑战，检验你的战术水平！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029180/extras/5d7729a2b384a18af05929c52a73a5db.avif?t=1768833137\" width=614 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029180/extras/609dde016a3eb9a49dcab3b971739325.poster.avif?t=1768833137\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029180/extras/609dde016a3eb9a49dcab3b971739325.webm?t=1768833137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029180/extras/609dde016a3eb9a49dcab3b971739325.mp4?t=1768833137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上神秘的未知版图，开启一场单人探险！收集多米诺牌以获得限定奖励，在这个专为探索与成长设计的沉浸式单人战役模式中建立你的帝国。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029180/extras/b5f4d5778aa3d5d4b96188a3ff1bd85e.avif?t=1768833137\" width=614 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参与季节性活动与每日挑战，加入我们欣欣向荣的玩家社区！与来自世界各地的玩家携手合作，解锁限时专属奖励。完成特殊任务目标，赢取社区积分；参与限时活动，与社区万众一心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029180/extras/ffff71e424bbe18dd874691a8526df4d.avif?t=1768833137\" width=614 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029180/extras/3fa9d6d571d19d1cda7fa49698fa11c9.poster.avif?t=1768833137\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029180/extras/3fa9d6d571d19d1cda7fa49698fa11c9.webm?t=1768833137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029180/extras/3fa9d6d571d19d1cda7fa49698fa11c9.mp4?t=1768833137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欣赏新、旧两个版本的《多米诺王国》美术风格。由宝琳·德特拉兹（Pauline Détraz）绘制的亮眼新画风和西里尔·布凯（Cyril Bouquet）创作的经典风格——二者任你挑选。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁并收集独特的角色指示物和城堡造型，让你的王国独一无二！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029180/extras/18df3f1b1d06193e7aacfbcb33ed3859.avif?t=1768833137\" width=614 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在各式设备上享受无缝的多人游戏体验，挑战使用 PC 或移动设备的朋友和对手——《多米诺王国》支持真正的跨平台兼容体验，你总能找到准备好与你开上一局的玩家！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法说明</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位玩家需要连接带有不同地形的多米诺牌地块，以此打造自己的王国。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每张多米诺牌都拥有两个方块，上面的地形可能相同也可能不同。某些牌上还带有王冠，可以让分数翻倍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从你的城堡地块开始放置多米诺牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家轮流挑选地形地块。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让相同地形（森林、田野、湖泊、山地）的地块彼此相连。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精心决策，扩张你的版图，打造包含多个王冠的广阔领地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >版图规模乘以王冠数量，即为领地的得分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每局游戏只需 10-20 分钟，无论是想快速来一局，还是花上数个小时打磨你的策略，《多米诺王国》都是完美的选择！</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 波兰语, 俄语, 日语, 简体中文, 匈牙利语, 韩语",
